  <brief_title>Right Ventricular Damage in Cardiovascular Magnetic Resonance</brief_title>
  <official_title>Right Ventricular Damage in ST-Elevation Myocardial Infarction. Risk Stratification by Visualization of Wall Motion, Edema and Delayed Enhancement Cardiovascular Magnetic Resonance</official_title>
